frames.caption: A helicopter hovers above a bustling city street at sunset, carrying a large object suspended below. A crowd of people gathers below, gazing upwards at the spectacle. The scene is framed by towering skyscrapers reflecting the warm hues of the setting sun.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a city street during sunset, with a helicopter carrying an object and a crowd of people watching. The setting is urban, surrounded by tall buildings.

frames.caption: A helicopter hovers above a bustling city street, carrying a large black bag suspended by a cable. The scene is set against a dramatic sunset, casting warm hues across the towering skyscrapers and the crowd below.
frames.description: The image captures an urban setting where a helicopter is flying low between skyscrapers, transporting a large bag. The sun is setting, creating a striking backdrop of orange and gold tones. A crowd of people is gathered on the street, observing the unusual aerial transport.
